      "text": "We are closely tracking Typhoon Sinlaku as it brings dangerous winds, heavy rain and flooding to Guam and the Northern Mariana Islands.\n\nI thank @POTUS for his quick approval of two emergency declarations this weekend providing federal resources and technical expertise to support territorial response efforts to this storm. \n \n@FEMA is fully engaged and has embedded response teams throughout the Pacific region who are coordinating requests for aid. @USCG is also activated and prepared to respond.\n\nFor those affected by the storm, our prayers are with you. Please stay safe and follow directions from local officials who are working around the clock to keep you safe.",
      "text_resolved": "We are closely tracking Typhoon Sinlaku as it brings dangerous winds, heavy rain and flooding to Guam and the Northern Mariana Islands.\n\nI thank @POTUS for his quick approval of two emergency declarations this weekend providing federal resources and technical expertise to support territorial response efforts to this storm. \n \n@FEMA is fully engaged and has embedded response teams throughout the Pacific region who are coordinating requests for aid. @USCG is also activated and prepared to respond.\n\nFor those affected by the storm, our prayers are with you. Please stay safe and follow directions from local officials who are working around the clock to keep you safe.",
